{"tid":1186288,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"昆頓塔倫天奴有意思拍《黑殺令》後續 Crossover黑俠梭羅","createTime":"2019-06-04T23:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T01:42:23.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0770013607bffbde4c2cea1784c99e5af14979","tid":1186288,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T23:13:38.000Z","msg":"荷里活鬼才導演昆頓塔倫天奴（Quentin Tarantino）上月受訪時表示新作《從前，有個荷里活》（Once Upon a Time...in Hollywood）是其從影以來的第9部作品，而他一生只想拍10部片，所以下部將會是最後一部。近日有指他想拍由自己編劇的DC漫畫《Django/Zorro》，漫畫中，他將著名20年代創作的虛構小說英雄西班牙劍客梭羅（Zorro）與其創作的西部片《黑殺令》（Django Unchained）男主角Django Freeman crossover。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190604/photo/bkn-20190604140011854-0604_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190604140412\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190604%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190604140011854-0604_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190604140412&h=82d0f374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190604/mobile/bkn-20190604140011854-0604_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190604%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190604140011854-0604_00862_001.html&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL8yzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=a903cd01\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190604/mobile/bkn-20190604140011854-0604_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7949ad993756bbd0a5b9e4806afee07cb2ad296c","tid":1186288,"uid":14802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:42:23.000Z","msg":"最後變<br />\n索女喪屍機關槍 <br />\n玩命飛車殺人狂啲fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"}]}